NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
SEARCH_ENGINE_URL=
CRON_SECRET=
```

### Variables Opcionales
```env
TOKKO_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_CREDENTIALS_PATH=
